name: Lead Closure TAT
query:
select
name,
lead_name as "Customer Name::200",
open_time as "Open Time::200",
call_done_time as "Call Done Time::200",
meeting_scheduled_time as "Meeting Scheduled Time::200",
meeting_conducted_time as "Meeting Conducted Time::200",
partly_documents_collected_time as "Partly Documents Collected Time::200",
documents_received_time as "Documents Received Time::200",
lender_selection_time as "Lender Selection Time::200",
pending_for_reporting_manager_approval_time as "Pending For Reporting Manager Approval Time::200",
login_done_time as "Login Done Time::200",
additional_doc_required_time as "Additional Doc Required Time::200",
disbursement_doc_list_time as "Disbursement Doc List Time::200",
disbursed_time as "Disbursed Time::200",
amount_credited_time as "Amount Credited Time::200"

from `tabLead`
order by name
